oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Boyd farmhouse
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Exterior view of a farmhouse on the Boyd property. Some people are posed outside the entrance of the building and others are standing in the foreground. Pigs, horses and a mule are outside the building.
